  <h4><em>Powerful mixin</em></h2>
  <p>We provide a powerful mixin for you to create more buttons, so if you feel like going this way, you can just invoke the mixin like shown below, and send some variables to meet your needs.</p>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="six columns">
<pre>
<code class="language-scss" data-language="scss">
  .custom-button {
    @include button($background-color: #1abc9c);
  }
</code>
</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="six columns">
<pre>
<code class="language-markup" data-language="markup">
  &lt;a href="#" class="my-super-button">Button&lt;/a>
</code>
</pre>
        </div>
      </div>

